  when  planet Q  The answer must be a place where you can buy new soap. Supermarket is a common place to buy soap. Washing is an action, not a place. Cabinet is a place to store soap, but not to obtain new soap. Own home is a general place, but not a specific place to obtain new soap. Sink is not a place to obtain new soap, it's a place to use soap. So the answer is supermarket (a).

